Sentencas: Nb2O5 doped BaCoO3-delta was synthesized using traditional solid-state reaction method.
Titulo: BaCo1-xNbxO3-δ as a Promising Cathode for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The electrochemical performance, physical properties and rate-determining step of BaCo1-xNbxO3-delta as a cathode material for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs) were investigated.
Titulo: BaCo1-xNbxO3-δ as a Promising Cathode for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The introduction of Nb in BaCo0.8Nb0.2O3-delta(BCN20)brings a stable cubic phase and a relative lower TEC (similar to 16.94x10-6 K-1) compared BCN20 with other Co-based perovskites.
Titulo: BaCo1-xNbxO3-δ as a Promising Cathode for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The oxygen vacancy concentration (delta) for BCN20 symmetrical cell is 0.153.
Titulo: BaCo1-xNbxO3-δ as a Promising Cathode for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The area specific resistance (ASR) of BCN20 symmetrical cell is merely 0.0397 omega center dot cm(2) at 700 degrees C. Base on the above findings, BCN20 has a great electrochemical performance as a cathode material for IT-SOFCs.
Titulo: BaCo1-xNbxO3-δ as a Promising Cathode for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Furthermore, we studies the reaction mechanism of BCN20 and concluded that desorption and diffusion of oxygen molecules is the oxygen reduction rate limiting step.
Titulo: BaCo1-xNbxO3-δ as a Promising Cathode for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Finally, full cell with BCN20 as cathode was tested and peak power density was measured to be 1042 m center dot cm(-2) at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: BaCo1-xNbxO3-δ as a Promising Cathode for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
